                        <head>Askold Ivantchik</head>
                        <p>This is the first electronic edition of the inscriptions from Tyras and its vicinity, from the Northern Black Sea
                            (IOSPE<hi rend="superscript">3</hi> vol. I). The introduction, editions and commentary are by Askold Ivantchik,
                            English translations are by Irene Polinskaya. The inscriptions were encoded following
                            the <ref target="http://epidoc.sf.net/">EpiDoc</ref> Guidelines for use of XML for ancient
                            documentary editions, and the website and supporting materials are the work of Gabriel Bodard,
                            Irene Polinskaya and colleagues at the Department of Digital Humanities, King's College London.</p>
                        
                        <div>
